<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Git GitHub - Guia R√°pido</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Oxygen', 'Ubuntu', 'Cantarell', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: clamp(8px, 2vw, 24px);
            color: #1a1a1a;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-size: clamp(13px, 1.5vw, 16px);
            min-height: 100vh;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: min(100%, 1200px);
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: clamp(12px, 2vw, 20px);
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f64f59, #c471ed, #12c2e9);
            padding: clamp(16px, 3vw, 32px);
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: clamp(20px, 4vw, 32px);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: clamp(11px, 2vw, 15px);
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .content-wrapper {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 0;
        }

        /* Layout para tablets e desktops */
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .content-wrapper {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
            }

            .section {
                border-right: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            }

            .section:nth-child(2n) {
                border-right: none;
            }
        }

        /* Layout para telas grandes */
        @media (min-width: 1200px) {
            .content-wrapper {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
        }

        .section {
            padding: clamp(14px, 2.5vw, 24px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        .section:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: clamp(14px, 2vw, 18px);
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: clamp(8px, 1.5vw, 14px);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: clamp(16px, 2.5vw, 20px);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .subsection {
            margin-bottom: clamp(10px, 2vw, 16px);
        }

        .subsection:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #444;
            margin-bottom: clamp(6px, 1vw, 10px);
            font-size: clamp(12px, 1.8vw, 15px);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .code-block {
            background: #2d2d2d;
            color: #f8f8f2;
            padding: clamp(8px, 1.5vw, 14px);
            border-radius: clamp(4px, 0.8vw, 8px);
            font-family: 'Consolas', 'Monaco', 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: clamp(11px, 1.4vw, 14px);
            margin: clamp(6px, 1vw, 10px) 0;
            overflow-x: auto;
            white-space: pre;
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
        }

        /* Scrollbar personalizada para Chrome, Edge, Opera */
        .code-block::-webkit-scrollbar {
            height: 8px;
        }

        .code-block::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .code-block::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #667eea;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .code-block::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: #7b8fef;
        }

        .command {
            color: #50fa7b;
        }

        .comment {
            color: #6272a4;
        }

        .note {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: clamp(8px, 1.5vw, 12px);
            margin: clamp(6px, 1vw, 10px) 0;
            font-size: clamp(11px, 1.4vw, 13px);
            border-radius: clamp(3px, 0.6vw, 6px);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .warning {
            background: #f8d7da;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
            padding: clamp(8px, 1.5vw, 12px);
            margin: clamp(6px, 1vw, 10px) 0;
            font-size: clamp(11px, 1.4vw, 13px);
            border-radius: clamp(3px, 0.6vw, 6px);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .steps {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: clamp(8px, 1.5vw, 14px);
            border-radius: clamp(4px, 0.8vw, 8px);
            margin: clamp(6px, 1vw, 10px) 0;
        }

        .step {
            margin: clamp(6px, 1vw, 8px) 0;
            padding-left: clamp(18px, 3vw, 24px);
            position: relative;
            font-size: clamp(11px, 1.5vw, 14px);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .step:before {
            content: "‚Üí";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: clamp(14px, 2vw, 16px);
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: clamp(2px, 0.4vw, 4px) clamp(6px, 1vw, 10px);
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: clamp(9px, 1.2vw, 12px);
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 4px;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .terminal {
            background: #1e1e1e;
            color: #d4d4d4;
            padding: clamp(8px, 1.5vw, 14px);
            border-radius: clamp(4px, 0.8vw, 8px);
            font-family: 'Consolas', 'Monaco', 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: clamp(11px, 1.4vw, 14px);
            margin: clamp(6px, 1vw, 10px) 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: auto;
            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
        }

        .terminal::-webkit-scrollbar {
            height: 8px;
        }

        .terminal::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #0a0a0a;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .terminal::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #667eea;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .prompt {
            color: #4ec9b0;
        }

        /* Ajustes para impress√£o */
        @media print {
            body {
                background: white;
                padding: 0;
            }

            .container {
                box-shadow: none;
                max-width: 100%;
            }

            .section {
                page-break-inside: avoid;
            }
        }

        /* Ajustes espec√≠ficos para telas pequenas */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            body {
                padding: 8px;
            }

            .code-block,
            .terminal {
                font-size: 10px;
            }
        }

        /* Ajustes para telas m√©dias (tablets) */
        @media (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 1024px) {
            .container {
                max-width: 95%;
            }
        }

        /* Ajustes para monitores grandes */
        @media (min-width: 1440px) {
            body {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .container {
                max-width: 1400px;
            }
        }

        /* Suporte para modo escuro do sistema */
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            /* Mant√©m as cores originais, mas voc√™ pode adicionar um tema escuro aqui se desejar */
        }

        /* Otimiza√ß√£o para touch */
        @media (hover: none) and (pointer: coarse) {
            .step,
            .note,
            .warning {
                padding: 12px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üöÄ Git & GitHub</h1>
            <p>Guia Completo para Terminal & VS Code (LXQt)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title"><span class="icon">üîë</span> 1. Configura√ß√£o Inicial</div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle">Configurar usu√°rio</div>
                    <div class="code-block"><span class="command">git config --global user.name "Seu Nome"</span>
<span class="command">git config --global user.email "seu@email.com"</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title"><span class="icon">üîê</span> 2. Autentica√ß√£o</div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle">Via SSH (Recomendado)</div>
                    <div class="steps">
                        <div class="step">Gerar chave SSH</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="code-block"><span class="command">ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C "seu@email.com"</span>
<span class="comment"># Pressione Enter 3x</span></div>

                    <div class="steps">
                        <div class="step">Copiar chave p√∫blica</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="code-block"><span class="command">cat ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub</span>
<span class="comment"># Copie toda a sa√≠da</span></div>

                    <div class="steps">
                        <div class="step">No GitHub: Settings ‚Üí SSH and GPG keys ‚Üí New SSH key</div>
                        <div class="step">Cole a chave e salve</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle">Via Token (HTTPS)</div>
                    <div class="steps">
                        <div class="step">GitHub: Settings ‚Üí Developer settings ‚Üí Personal access tokens ‚Üí Tokens (classic)</div>
                        <div class="step">Generate new token ‚Üí Marque "repo"</div>
                        <div class="step">Copie o token gerado</div>
                        <div class="step">Use como senha no git push</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title"><span class="icon">üì§</span> 3. Primeiro Envio ao GitHub</div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle"><span class="badge">Terminal</span></div>
                    <div class="code-block"><span class="comment"># Inicializar reposit√≥rio</span>
<span class="command">git init</span>

<span class="comment"># Adicionar arquivos</span>
<span class="command">git add .</span>

<span class="comment"># Fazer commit</span>
<span class="command">git commit -m "primeiro commit"</span>

<span class="comment"># Conectar ao GitHub (SSH)</span>
<span class="command">git remote add origin git@github.com:usuario/repo.git</span>

<span class="comment"># OU via HTTPS</span>
<span class="command">git remote add origin https://github.com/usuario/repo.git</span>

<span class="comment"># Enviar para GitHub</span>
<span class="command">git branch -M main</span>
<span class="command">git push -u origin main</span></div>
                </div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle"><span class="badge">VS Code</span></div>
                    <div class="steps">
                        <div class="step">Abra a pasta do projeto</div>
                        <div class="step">Ctrl+Shift+G (Source Control)</div>
                        <div class="step">Clique em "Initialize Repository"</div>
                        <div class="step">Clique no "+" em Changes (stage all)</div>
                        <div class="step">Digite mensagem e Commit (‚úì)</div>
                        <div class="step">Clique em "..." ‚Üí Remote ‚Üí Add Remote</div>
                        <div class="step">Cole a URL do reposit√≥rio</div>
                        <div class="step">Clique em "..." ‚Üí Push</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title"><span class="icon">üîÑ</span> 4. Enviar Altera√ß√µes</div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle"><span class="badge">Terminal</span></div>
                    <div class="code-block"><span class="comment"># Ver o que mudou</span>
<span class="command">git status</span>

<span class="comment"># Adicionar altera√ß√µes</span>
<span class="command">git add .</span>
<span class="comment"># OU arquivo espec√≠fico</span>
<span class="command">git add arquivo.js</span>

<span class="comment"># Fazer commit</span>
<span class="command">git commit -m "descri√ß√£o das mudan√ßas"</span>

<span class="comment"># Enviar</span>
<span class="command">git push</span></div>
                </div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle"><span class="badge">VS Code</span></div>
                    <div class="steps">
                        <div class="step">Ctrl+Shift+G</div>
                        <div class="step">Clique no "+" nos arquivos modificados</div>
                        <div class="step">Digite mensagem e Commit</div>
                        <div class="step">Clique em "Sync Changes" ou "Push"</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title"><span class="icon">üìä</span> 5. Ver Status e Hist√≥rico</div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle">Status (mudan√ßas locais)</div>
                    <div class="code-block"><span class="command">git status</span>
<span class="comment"># Mostra arquivos modificados, staged, etc</span></div>
                </div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle">Log (hist√≥rico de commits)</div>
                    <div class="code-block"><span class="comment"># Formato simples</span>
<span class="command">git log --oneline</span>

<span class="comment"># Formato completo</span>
<span class="command">git log</span>

<span class="comment"># √öltimos 5 commits</span>
<span class="command">git log -5</span>

<span class="comment"># Com gr√°fico de branches</span>
<span class="command">git log --graph --oneline --all</span></div>
                </div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle"><span class="badge">VS Code</span></div>
                    <div class="steps">
                        <div class="step">Status: Ctrl+Shift+G</div>
                        <div class="step">Log: "..." ‚Üí View History</div>
                        <div class="step">Ou instale extens√£o "Git History"</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title"><span class="icon">üì•</span> 6. Baixar Reposit√≥rio (Clone)</div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle"><span class="badge">Terminal</span></div>
                    <div class="code-block"><span class="comment"># Via SSH</span>
<span class="command">git clone git@github.com:usuario/repo.git</span>

<span class="comment"># Via HTTPS</span>
<span class="command">git clone https://github.com/usuario/repo.git</span>

<span class="comment"># Clone para pasta espec√≠fica</span>
<span class="command">git clone URL nome-da-pasta</span></div>
                </div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle"><span class="badge">VS Code</span></div>
                    <div class="steps">
                        <div class="step">Ctrl+Shift+P ‚Üí "Git: Clone"</div>
                        <div class="step">Cole a URL do reposit√≥rio</div>
                        <div class="step">Escolha a pasta de destino</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title"><span class="icon">‚¨áÔ∏è</span> 7. Baixar Altera√ß√µes do GitHub</div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle"><span class="badge">Terminal</span></div>
                    <div class="code-block"><span class="comment"># Baixar e aplicar mudan√ßas</span>
<span class="command">git pull</span>

<span class="comment"># OU em 2 passos:</span>
<span class="command">git fetch</span>  <span class="comment"># Baixa mudan√ßas</span>
<span class="command">git merge origin/main</span>  <span class="comment"># Aplica mudan√ßas</span></div>
                </div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle"><span class="badge">VS Code</span></div>
                    <div class="steps">
                        <div class="step">Ctrl+Shift+G</div>
                        <div class="step">Clique em "..." ‚Üí Pull</div>
                        <div class="step">Ou clique no √≠cone de sincroniza√ß√£o (‚Üª)</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title"><span class="icon">‚ö†Ô∏è</span> 8. Resolver Conflitos</div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle">Como acontecem?</div>
                    <div class="note">Conflitos ocorrem quando voc√™ e outra pessoa editam a mesma parte do mesmo arquivo.</div>
                </div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle"><span class="badge">Terminal</span></div>
                    <div class="code-block"><span class="comment"># Ao fazer pull/merge, se houver conflito:</span>
<span class="command">git pull</span>
<span class="comment"># Mensagem: CONFLICT (content): Merge conflict</span>

<span class="comment"># Ver arquivos em conflito</span>
<span class="command">git status</span>

<span class="comment"># Abra o arquivo e procure por:</span>
<span class="comment"><<<<<<< HEAD
seu c√≥digo local
=======
c√≥digo do GitHub
>>>>>>> origem</span>

<span class="comment"># Edite o arquivo, escolha o que manter</span>
<span class="comment"># Remova as marca√ß√µes <<<, ===, >>></span>

<span class="comment"># Ap√≥s resolver:</span>
<span class="command">git add arquivo-resolvido.js</span>
<span class="command">git commit -m "resolvido conflito"</span>
<span class="command">git push</span></div>
                </div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle"><span class="badge">VS Code</span></div>
                    <div class="steps">
                        <div class="step">VS Code detecta conflitos automaticamente</div>
                        <div class="step">Arquivos em conflito ter√£o √≠cone "!"</div>
                        <div class="step">Abra o arquivo, ver√° op√ß√µes:</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="note">
                        ‚Ä¢ Accept Current Change (seu c√≥digo)<br>
                        ‚Ä¢ Accept Incoming Change (do GitHub)<br>
                        ‚Ä¢ Accept Both Changes<br>
                        ‚Ä¢ Compare Changes
                    </div>
                    <div class="steps">
                        <div class="step">Escolha a op√ß√£o desejada</div>
                        <div class="step">Stage o arquivo resolvido</div>
                        <div class="step">Commit e Push</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <div class="subtitle">Dicas para evitar conflitos</div>
                    <div class="note">
                        ‚úì Sempre fa√ßa <strong>git pull</strong> antes de come√ßar a trabalhar<br>
                        ‚úì Fa√ßa commits pequenos e frequentes<br>
                        ‚úì Comunique-se com a equipe sobre arquivos em edi√ß√£o
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title"><span class="icon">üí°</span> 9. Comandos √öteis</div>

                <div class="code-block"><span class="comment"># Desfazer √∫ltimo commit (mant√©m altera√ß√µes)</span>
<span class="command">git reset --soft HEAD~1</span>

<span class="comment"># Descartar mudan√ßas locais de um arquivo</span>
<span class="command">git checkout -- arquivo.js</span>

<span class="comment"># Ver diferen√ßas antes de commitar</span>
<span class="command">git diff</span>

<span class="comment"># Ver branches</span>
<span class="command">git branch</span>

<span class="comment"># Criar e mudar para nova branch</span>
<span class="command">git checkout -b nova-branch</span>

<span class="comment"># Ver URL do remote</span>
<span class="command">git remote -v</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title"><span class="icon">üéØ</span> 10. Fluxo de Trabalho T√≠pico</div>

                <div class="terminal">
<span class="prompt">$</span> git pull                    <span class="comment"># Atualizar</span>
<span class="prompt">$</span> <span class="comment"># ... fazer altera√ß√µes ...</span>
<span class="prompt">$</span> git status                 <span class="comment"># Ver mudan√ßas</span>
<span class="prompt">$</span> git add .                  <span class="comment"># Adicionar tudo</span>
<span class="prompt">$</span> git commit -m "mensagem"  <span class="comment"># Commitar</span>
<span class="prompt">$</span> git push                   <span class="comment"># Enviar</span></div>

                <div class="warning">
                    <strong>‚ö° Lembre-se:</strong> Sempre fa√ßa <strong>pull</strong> antes de <strong>push</strong> para evitar conflitos!
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
